Clarivest Asset Management LLC Lifted Its Holding in Ingredion INC (INGR) by $21.51 Million as Market Valuation Declined

July 27, 2017 - By Henry Gaston

Investors sentiment is 1.09 in 2016 Q4. Its the same as in 2016Q3. It is without change, as 41 investors sold INGR shares while 156 reduced holdings. only 52 funds opened positions while 162 raised stakes. 59.87 million shares or 1.89% less from 61.03 million shares in 2016Q3 were reported. Fincl Counselors Inc has invested 0.02% in Ingredion Inc (NYSE:INGR). Cadence Mgmt Limited Liability Company holds 0.06% of its portfolio in Ingredion Inc (NYSE:INGR) for 6,852 shares. Principal Financial Grp Incorporated owns 686,400 shares. Assetmark invested 0% in Ingredion Inc (NYSE:INGR). Princeton Alpha Mgmt Ltd Partnership holds 0.24% in Ingredion Inc (NYSE:INGR) or 9,170 shares. Wellington Mngmt Gru Ltd Liability Partnership invested 0.03% of its portfolio in Ingredion Inc (NYSE:INGR). Canada Pension Plan Board holds 0.12% in Ingredion Inc (NYSE:INGR) or 262,495 shares. Tudor Invest Corporation Et Al reported 7,544 shares or 0.02% of all its holdings. Stanley has invested 0.14% in Ingredion Inc (NYSE:INGR). Nomura Asset Management Comm Limited reported 8,670 shares. Synovus Financial Corporation reported 45 shares. Invesco Ltd stated it has 502,838 shares or 0.02% of all its holdings. Profund Advsrs Ltd has 12,035 shares. Contravisory Invest Mgmt invested 3.48% in Ingredion Inc (NYSE:INGR). Chevy Chase Tru Inc holds 0% of its portfolio in Ingredion Inc (NYSE:INGR) for 3,750 shares.
Clarivest Asset Management Llc increased its stake in Ingredion Inc (INGR) by 9050.03% based on its latest 2016Q4 regulatory filing with the SEC. Clarivest Asset Management Llc bought 173,489 shares as the company’s stock declined 4.33% while stock markets rallied. The institutional investor held 175,406 shares of the packaged foods company at the end of 2016Q4, valued at $21.92M, up from 1,917 at the end of the previous reported quarter. Clarivest Asset Management Llc who had been investing in Ingredion Inc for a number of months, seems to be bullish on the $8.78B market cap company. The stock declined 0.52% or $0.64 reaching $122.43 on the news. About 166,282 shares traded. Ingredion Inc (NYSE:INGR) has declined 2.30% since July 27, 2016 and is downtrending. It has underperformed by 19.00% the S&P500.






Clarivest Asset Management Llc, which manages about $3.41B and $3.75B US Long portfolio, decreased its stake in Steel Dynamics Inc (NASDAQ:STLD) by 141,180 shares to 1.15 million shares, valued at $40.87 million in 2016Q4, according to the filing. It also reduced its holding in At&T Inc (NYSE:T) by 332,467 shares in the quarter, leaving it with 419,977 shares, and cut its stake in Disney Walt Co (NYSE:DIS). 
More recent Ingredion Inc (NYSE:INGR) news were published by: Benzinga.com which released: “5 Undervalued Stocks That Could Trade 20% Higher” on July 26, 2017. Also Foodbusinessnews.net published the news titled: “Ingredion to expand South Carolina operations” on July 27, 2017. Postandcourier.com‘s news article titled: “North Charleston food, beverage ingredient maker expanding operations” with publication date: July 21, 2017 was also an interesting one.
Ingredion Inc (NYSE:INGR) Ratings Coverage
Among 7 analysts covering Ingredion Inc (NYSE:INGR), 4 have Buy rating, 1 Sell and 2 Hold. Therefore 57% are positive. Ingredion Inc had 15 analyst reports since August 3, 2015 according to SRatingsIntel. The rating was initiated by Jefferies on Wednesday, December 16 with “Buy”. The firm has “Buy” rating given on Wednesday, June 14 by Jefferies. Stephens upgraded Ingredion Inc (NYSE:INGR) on Friday, January 29 to “Overweight” rating. BMO Capital Markets maintained Ingredion Inc (NYSE:INGR) on Thursday, April 13 with “Hold” rating. The rating was upgraded by Citigroup to “Buy” on Monday, September 14. The rating was initiated by Societe Generale with “Hold” on Thursday, September 8. Citigroup maintained Ingredion Inc (NYSE:INGR) rating on Wednesday, June 15. Citigroup has “Buy” rating and $140 target. The rating was maintained by Jefferies with “Buy” on Thursday, June 29. Jefferies maintained the stock with “Buy” rating in Friday, May 26 report. BMO Capital Markets maintained Ingredion Inc (NYSE:INGR) on Friday, October 30 with “Market Perform” rating.


