All the key data for a company in one view














Instantly profile the performance and constituents of a selected industry














Take a fresh look at macroeconomic data














Perform earnings and profitability analysis with an interactive income statement














Monitor and Analyze – understand portfolio performance in real-time and quantify portfolio risk





































			Get straight to the opportunities

With access to global news, commentary and data from all markets and asset classes, Thomson Reuters Eikon is the natural environment for researching investment management opportunities and monitoring your holdings – a vast resource of quality global content and the tools to make immediate sense of it.
With Eikon, you can see the outliers straight away; you can focus instantly on where the action is, and make meaningful comparisons with the next click.
Our exclusive StarMine analytics and predictive modeling, for example, help you anticipate surprises and identify opportunity. Fundamentals cover 99% of the global market capitalization and I/B/E/S Estimates deliver clear and trusted insight.
Eikon is designed to suit the way you work, intuitively moving from task to task. Navigate through coverage lists or portfolios with ease, and analyze securities more efficiently.







			The way you work

Monitor the markets
See every significant change that affects your portfolios, including price and technical signals, news, events and research. Set alerts so you know instantly, even when logged out. Compare economic indicators and predict possible macro surprises.
Screen companies and generate ideas
Screen 60,000 public companies globally using a wide range of criteria (6,000 data items). Sort and review the results to create a target list for further analysis. 
Value companies quickly and effectively
Examine details – from fundamentals to predictive analytics, from research and estimates to events and ownership – to find insights and opportunities.
Share research and recommendations
Load and tag internal research for easy access and sharing with your colleagues and across your firm. 
Align portfolios with investment objectives
Built-in portfolio analytics help you quickly understand the sources of relative risk and return in your funded and model portfolios. Adjust portfolios efficiently; inform clients clearly and accurately.







			View companies in context and in depth

Fundamentals
Standardized and company-specific fundamentals data, with quantitative analysis tools.
Thomson Reuters I/B/E/S Estimates
More history, contributing brokers and company coverage than anywhere else.
Industry-specific metrics
Over 200 key performance indicators across Airlines, Banking and Finance, Energy and Mining, Insurance, Pharmaceuticals and Healthcare, Real Estate, Hotels and Homebuilders, Retail and Restaurants, Technology and Telecommunications.
Research
From 800 active sources, covering more than 21,000 companies across 87 countries. Thomson Reuters StarMine provides analyst ratings for estimates and recommendations.
Events
A single point for the fastest possible access to market-moving corporate disclosures and brokerage events.
Ownership
The most comprehensive global share ownership and profiles data available.
Predictive analytics and models
Thomson Reuters StarMine proprietary algorithms lead to more accurate estimates and generate rich inputs to predictive models.
 













